# TypeScript

## Config

Extends `astro/tsconfigs/strict`. Path alias: `@/*` → `src/*`.

## Naming

See `naming-conventions.mdc` for function, file, type, and component naming rules.

## Imports

- All imports at top of file — no inline imports
- Prettier sorts imports (`@/` first) — run formatter before commit
- Single quotes for strings (Prettier default); use double quotes when string contains `'`

## Switch exhaustiveness

For discriminated unions/enums, use `never` in default:

```ts
switch (layout) {
  case 'text-left': ...
  case 'img-left': ...
  default: {
    const _exhaustive: never = layout;
    return _exhaustive;
  }
}
```

## Types

- Locale: `'da' | 'en'` from `@/lib/i18n`
- API routes: `APIRoute` from `astro`
- Strapi responses: typed generics on fetch helpers; refine types incrementally
- Avoid `any` in new code — prefer explicit interfaces in `src/lib/`

## Server vs client boundary

| Server-only | Client-safe |
|---|---|
| `@/lib/strapi/client` | `@/lib/i18n`, `@/lib/nav-config`, `@/lib/utils` |
| `@/lib/si/client` | Props passed from Astro parent |
| `@/lib/mailgun` | |
